Notes: SP snaps 14-game losing streak at UW-Stout with first win since 12/9/89...SP's
Scott and Schultz both had career scoring highs and Heuer had career-high in
rebounds...SP had three starters with three fouls at halftime...SP's Schultz
hit two free throws with 46 seconds left to break 73-73 tie.
